query:
/*+ NoMergeJoin(mi mi_idx t ci) */ select count(*)
from title AS t
inner join movie_info_idx AS mi_idx
on t.id = mi_idx.movie_id AND t.production_year > 2008 AND t.production_year < 2014 AND mi_idx.info_type_id = 101
inner join movie_info AS mi
on t.id = mi.movie_id AND mi.info_type_id = 3
inner join cast_info AS ci
on t.id = ci.movie_id;
